            <div type="transcript" id="F86A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>For every Bird a nest -</l>
                    <l>Wherefore in timid quest </l>
                    <l>Some little Wren goes seeking round - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Wherefore when boughs are free, </l>
                    <l>Households in every tree,</l>
                    <l>Pilgrim be found?  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Perhaps a home too high - </l>
                    <l>Ah aristocracy!  </l>
                    <l>The little Wren desires - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Perhaps of twig so fine -</l>
                    <l>Of twine e'en superfine, </l>
                    <l>Her pride aspires - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Lark is not ashamed </l>
                    <l>To build opon the ground </l>
                    <l>Her modest house -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Yet who of all the throng </l>
                    <l>Dancing around the sun </l>
                    <l>Does so rejoice?  </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
